Foxtel will launch the third season of Orange is the New Black on Netflix on June 12 . 
  The cable TV company will screen the entire season in a marathon . 
  A kink in the agreement allows Foxtel to offer the series as an on-demand streaming title . 
  The third season premieres on Netflix in the US on the same day . 
  Netflix has a pre-existing distribution deal in Australia . 
  In Australia, this means every episode of the prison drama will be shown in one marathon . 
 